  }, "https://github.com/dltxio/idem-mobile"), "\xA0"))), mdx("p", null, "Fundamentally, the objective is to create an \u2018Ai OS\u2019 built into a \u2018box\u2019 that provides support for \u2018webizen\u2019 which is intended to become a class of AI Agents that significantly influence the future of human / societal / cyber - interactions (and in-turn also, support for human rights, law, etc.).\xA0"), mdx("p", null, "In-effect, its like a digital vault, personal cloud platform; with a primary interface being an AI Agent - that\u2019s called a \u2018webizen\u2019, that is defined via standards; to be an extensible platform for the distribution of\xA0 AI related software, that improves a persons \u2018Webizen\u2019 functionality."), mdx("h3", {
